{"id":273761,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-数十名各地上访维权者抗议凤凰网删帖（/","date":"2013-01-09T13:01:41Z","modified":"2013-01-09T13:01:41Z","title":"维权网 | 数十名各地上访维权者抗议凤凰网删帖（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员田静民报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，数十名各地上访维权人士因凤凰网无故大量删除反腐维权的帖子、封用户名而抗议，并为凤凰网制作了一面“删帖英雄，官网勾结”的“锦旗”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>近两年以来，凤凰网大量删除了上访维权人士的反腐败的帖子。如</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、网民邓志波于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>在凤凰网网罗天下和新闻贴图两个板块的帖子《血泪的举报》全部被删；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、网民用户名航天牛于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>在有料天天报、网罗天下和新闻贴图三个板块的帖子《最高法院的阴阳卷》和</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>日</span><span>发表的《国法保护谁？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>岁儿童维权</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>年》以上四个帖子在元旦期间全部被删。另在有料天天报发表的《中纪委领导</span><span> </span><span>最高法院审案四年没有结果是违纪还是违法？》于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日</span><span>贺国强视察中纪委信访的当天被删；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>、航母</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5486</span><span>在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>发表的《最高法院的公章哪去了》于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>被删掉。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>为了行使揭露腐败、监督政府和言论自由的权利，大家要求凤凰网公开在网上向网民赔礼道歉，恢复被删的帖子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加抗议活动的有来自各地的上访维权人士：上海：程桂兰、朱萍萍、吴玉芬、周炎、孔令珍、韦开贞、郑培陪、赵广军；天津：郑建慧；河北：王心灵、段淑兰、张敬泉；江苏：邵云黎；吉林：邓志波、董奎红；湖北：江富有；陕西：吕动力；河南：王群凤、史秋菊；辽宁：刘力、王淑娥；武汉：何贵先、徐崇阳等数十人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TXy66Xzl3qs/UOz-Aq306lI/AAAAAAAAYj4/lphQq1IpupM/s1600/011.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-TXy66Xzl3qs/UOz-Aq306lI/AAAAAAAAYj4/lphQq1IpupM/s320/011.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ngI0UlcIn30/UOz-BRDPsfI/AAAAAAAAYj8/brEYl7mgCAE/s1600/018.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-ngI0UlcIn30/UOz-BRDPsfI/AAAAAAAAYj8/brEYl7mgCAE/s320/018.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e5tAZxk-Ueo/UOz-CDPd2OI/AAAAAAAAYkA/YdUCP87kmeY/s1600/016.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-e5tAZxk-Ueo/UOz-CDPd2OI/AAAAAAAAYkA/YdUCP87kmeY/s320/016.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[171,16910,10830,9212]}